	* configure.ac (--with-config-file): If nothing is specified, use
	/etc/GNUstep/GNUstep.conf if the prefix is /, /usr or
	/usr/GNUstep, and $prefix/etc/GNUstep/GNUstep.conf in other cases.
	Updated documentation.
