	* filesystem.csh.in: Fixed typo (GNUSTEP_SYSTEM_ROOT instead of
	GNUSTEP_SYSTEM_APPS).
	* configure.ac: Updated comments avoiding references to
	GNUSTEP_SYSTEM_ROOT.
